                    students, sharing his expertise and fostering a supportive learning environment within the university community. His commitment to excellence and his drive
                    for continuous improvement position him as a future leader in the IT industry.
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="item">
                <img src="~/Content/Images/drei.jpg" alt="Image 2">
                <div class="description">
                    <div class="name">Alexandrei Dalisay</div>
                    Alexandrei is an Information Technology student at the Polytechnic University of the Philippines (PUP) with a strong technical acumen and a flair for creative
                    problem-solving. Known for his proficiency in multiple programming languages and frameworks, Sarah excels in developing innovative software applications that
                    address complex issues. She has a proven track record of success in academic projects, where she applies her technical skills to deliver high-quality solutions
                    on time. Sarah is also actively involved in tech communities and enjoys sharing knowledge through workshops and seminars. Her dedication to her craft and her
                    passion for technology make her a valuable asset to any team or organization.
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="item">
                <img src="~/Content/Images/red.png"  alt="Image 3">
                <div class="description">
                    <div class="name">Justine Redinz Mendoza</div>
                    Justine Redinz Mendoza is an Information Technology student at the Polytechnic University of the Philippines (PUP) who combines technical expertise with a
                    creative approach to problem-solving. With a keen interest in software development and data analysis, Emily has successfully completed various projects that
                    demonstrate her ability to apply theoretical knowledge to practical scenarios. She is adept at working in team environments and is known for her effective
                    communication skills and collaborative spirit. Emily is also passionate about encouraging more women to pursue careers in technology and actively mentors
                    female students in her community. Her commitment to excellence and innovation positions her as a future leader in the tech industry.
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="item">
                <img src="~/Content/Images/aaron.jpg"  alt="Image 4">
                <div class="description">
                    <div class="name">Aaron Rebuluanan</div>
                    Aaron is an Information Technology student at the Polytechnic University of the Philippines (PUP) with a passion for cybersecurity and network administration.
                    His academic journey is marked by a series of successful projects that showcase his technical proficiency and his ability to develop robust security solutions.
                    Michael is dedicated to staying updated with the latest advancements in cybersecurity and actively participates in related workshops and conferences. He is also
                    a member of the university’s cybersecurity club, where he collaborates with peers to tackle real-world security challenges. Michael's analytical skills,
                    attention to detail, and commitment to safeguarding digital environments make him a promising professional in the field of cybersecurity.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <!-- Modal for User Type Selection -->
    <div class="modal fade" id="userTypeModal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="userTypeModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="modal-dialog" role="document">
            <div class="modal-content">
                <div class="modal-header">
                    <h5 class="modal-title" id="userTypeModalLabel">Select User Type</h5>
                    <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">
                        <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
                    </button>
                </div>
                <div class="modal-body">
                    <div class="user-type-option" onclick="selectUserType('Alumni')">
                        Alumni
                    </div>
                    <div class="user-type-option" onclick="selectUserType('Company')">
                        Company
                    </div>
                    <div class="user-type-option" onclick="selectUserType('Admin')">
                        Admin
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- jQuery first, then Popper.js, then Bootstrap JS -->
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.2.1.slim.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.11.0/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
